Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.61,0:00:15.65,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Huh, no, no, no!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.65,0:00:18.24,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Look, it’s not like you can control when you catch a cold!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.68,0:01:07.29,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Alright, let’s calm down!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:10.54,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Anyway, our performance today turned out great, didn’t it!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.86,0:01:40.86,Kaho,,0,0,0,,You know what we mean!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.86,0:01:45.58,Kaho,,0,0,0,,You being our acting leader really saved our performance!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.78,0:02:15.53,Kaho,,0,0,0,,You know, so much stuff happened while you were gone, Kozue-senpai.\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.58,0:02:23.38,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Yeah!\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:30.07,Kaho,,0,0,0,,…Actually, there was one thing I wanted to ask…\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:39.02,Kaho,,0,0,0,,I was wondering about your relationship with the student council president.\N{\fs35}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.07,0:00:04.38,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Um…\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.25,0:00:08.99,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Let me say it one more time.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.63,0:00:13.07,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I sincerely apologize for all the trouble I caused.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.65,0:00:20.72,Kozue,,0,0,0,,No, I definitely could have done better.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.72,0:00:25.07,Kozue,,0,0,0,,This just proves I have gotten too lax with my personal health management.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.07,0:00:28.59,Kozue,,0,0,0,,As your club president, this is something I cannot forgive myself for.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.04,0:00:42.02,Kozue,,0,0,0,,In any case!\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.62,0:00:43.66,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I’m very sorry!\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.72,0:01:04.30,Kozue,,0,0,0,,You two…!\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.20,0:01:13.01,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I… suppose.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.54,0:01:15.04,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which…\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.61,0:01:16.56,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Sayaka-san.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.57,0:01:20.61,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.03,0:01:22.21,Kozue,,0,0,0,,This was all thanks to you.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.11,0:02:16.97,Kozue,,0,0,0,,It seems so.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.43,0:02:22.26,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I’d like to hear that story sometime later. \NIt seems like it was quite an exciting adventure.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.43,0:02:32.46,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Yes?\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.90,0:02:40.83,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…Ah…\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.54,0:02:45.05,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Based on Tsuzuri and Megumi’s reactions, I presume?\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.91,0:02:48.57,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Well…\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.51,0:02:55.62,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I’d say at this point it’s been about a year since she left the School Idol Club.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.31,0:03:00.77,Kozue,,0,0,0,,We all loved her very much, so it made us very sad when she left.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.11,0:03:05.96,Kozue,,0,0,0,,But…\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.11,0:03:10.10,Kozue,,0,0,0,,right, let’s look at things from her perspective.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.10,0:03:16.13,Kozue,,0,0,0,,I’m sure that she had fun having the chance to be with her juniors after so long.\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:18.77,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Sometime soon…\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.07,0:03:22.69,Kozue,,0,0,0,,perhaps we might face her as well…\N{\fs35}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.69,0:03:24.69,Kozue,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.59,0:00:31.04,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Whoa, she’s serious about this.\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.03,0:00:49.81,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Wait, are you sure we can say “ok” here!?\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.81,0:00:52.68,Megumi,,0,0,0,,What happens if we catch a cold ourselves!?\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.09,0:00:58.36,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I mean, I guess so.\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.96,0:01:02.30,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Let’s accept it to shut her up, then!\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.24,0:01:35.09,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Good work out there, Sayaka-sama.\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.24,0:02:06.70,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Sun Goddess Sayaka.\N{\fs35}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.04,0:00:34.41,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Mad respect, Kozue-senpai…\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.41,0:00:37.63,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Ain’t no way I could live like that…\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.25,0:01:28.09,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Yeaaah. For real.\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.09,0:01:31.73,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Thank ya, Sayaka-sama~\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.01,0:01:57.46,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Huh!? Can we really accept your thanks!?\N{\fs35}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.12,0:00:40.50,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Why did you put it like that…?\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.12,0:01:19.11,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Huh? A-Ah, yes!\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.51,0:01:38.47,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Wha–!? U-Um, what do you mean!?\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.38,0:01:47.58,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Kaho-san…\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.01,0:01:52.52,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,No, I should thank you guys too.\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:02:02.71,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,W-Why are you putting me on some sort of pedestal!?\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.24,0:02:09.94,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,That wasn’t an invitation!\N{\fs35}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.02,0:00:44.65,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Ok.\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.13,0:00:55.67,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,If we don’t accept her apology, she won’t stop.\N{\fs35}[Tsuzuri]
